Text: Is it just the psychotic ingrate's who watch this show that don't say THANK YOU or are people who download your other torrents equally ungrateful?? I don't mean to sound self-rightous by any means. I just hope people realize that most torrents are uploaded by people who get nothing in return except for an occasional THANK YOU!!
Greetings again from Norway - txs for sharing, so we dont have to wait for the good stuff swimming over ;)
